data.description: Beautifully renovated 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom plus a den home in the heart of Fort Myers. Sprawling open concept, great space for entertaining, the kitchen features a large quartz island in the kitchen, Stainless Double oven, Monogram stainless steel dishwasher, stainless steel French door refrigerator. This home has tons of upgrades including a new roof in 2022, 2019 4-zone AC unit, new water softener/filtration system (RO under the kitchen sink), whole home generator hookup, new light fixtures in every room and brand-new washer/dryer and interior and exterior painting to give this home a fresh and modern look. Spacious fenced backyard with mature trees perfectly positioned on a corner lot for maximum privacy. Plenty of backyard space for a pool. This home is in a well established neighborhood close to restaurants, entertainment and the beaches. Make your showing appointment today!
